Description: Semantic XBRL is a dataset that contains RDF generated from the data submitted as XBRL to the U.S Securities and Exchange Commission (SEC).Semantic data is generated by translating XBRL to RDF using [OWL ontologies derived from the XBRL XML Schemas](http://rhizomik.net/ontologies/bizontos).
